'''Malcolm A. Lightman''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
** [[von Zedtwitz Life Master Pairs]] (1) 1945 

